q4 module¶

q4.plot_graph(file)¶

Plotting two different types of graphs.

Parameters

  • file – To read the command line file path

  • org_data – to read the csv file for graph 1

  • groups1 – Grouping the data by a values

  • method_data – to read the csv file for graph 2

Return type

Graph plot
